title: Dad vs. Traffic
description:
Written by James McCarthy
Starring Jonathan Marballi, Kelly Hudson, Langan Kingsley, Lisa Kleinman, Avery Monsen, Dan Hodapp

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, April 1, 2013.
